name: Bloody Valentine
description:
14th of February, 2022.

I thought i was dreaming..
i gave my heart to you and didn't know it'd be the end of me

Lovin' yesterday, Screamin' today.

Wish i would knew you'd turn our love into a war
so you left me to win.

I think i'm turning into a ghost
Even though I'm breathing I don't feel alive.

You be my bloody valentine tonight.
